
Manage source/annotation.rst by Ansible
=======================================


1) Setup (run only once to create first source/annotation.rst)
--------------------------------------------------------------

The following files are used to create first raw-annotation.yml

* Ansible playbook create-raw-annotation.yml
* List of files annotation-files.txt
* Ansible template raw-annotation.yml.j2

Copy created file raw-annotation.yml to annotation.yml

Run the playbook.yml in the directory doc. This will create
source/annotation.rst


2) Update source/annotation.rst
-------------------------------

Make changes in

* datafile annotation.yml
* Ansible template annotation.rst.j2

Run the playbook.yml in the directory doc. This will update
source/annotation.rst
--
